  "summary": [
    "Create official DEO letters directly from immutable Approved or Issued complaint reply revisions",
    "Preserve the supplied legal-size ODT layout, Punjab logo, two-column complaint/remarks table, signature and CC section",
    "Provide dedicated individual preparation, browser PDF preview, finalization and revised-letter supersession workflow",
    "Provide a searchable official-letter register with exact awaiting, preview, finalized and failure metrics",
    "Provide versioned ODT template management and configurable active/default signature profiles with effective dates",
    "Provide configurable letter number, date format, recipient, subject and CC defaults while enforcing unique diary numbers",
    "Generate both checksum-verified ODT and PDF artifacts and retain immutable complaint, reply, template and signature snapshots",
    "Use one approved-only official-letter engine for individual and batch generation; imported drafts are never eligible",
    "Expose official-letter actions from Reply Editor, Reply Queue and AI Reply Archive",
    "Run source contracts, Python compilation, migration, complete pytest suite and Astro production build by default with automatic rollback",
    "Update the legacy reply-workflow integration test to enforce the approved-only official-letter lifecycle without weakening production controls"
  ],
